Detailed Description

Keep track of prefixes that are actually registered with ccnd (as opposed to Filters used to dispatch interests).

There may be several filters for each registered prefix.

Waiter for prefixes being deregistered.

This is because we don't want to wait for the prefix to be deregistered normally, but if we try to re-register it we have to to avoid races.
